{"tid":1491877,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[開學日就快到]好擔心學生唔知發生乜事……","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:55.000Z","uid":310692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4213332b9be9fe9137c012f0244a78b4e213bfc","tid":1491877,"uid":310692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"各位&hellip;&hellip;小弟只是一個中學教畜&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我好擔心一個問題，好多北區、元屯天既中學有好多內地生，佢地根本就唔知香港人點解要抗爭，甚至覺得香港好亂、我地係度搞事。<br />\n基本上，我接觸既學生，如果係本地生，ok既，佢唔認同我地，都知政府垃圾；但內地生，就一面倒撐警！<br />\n唔好話開學搞罷課，我擔心開學之後，撐警或者不問世事既學生會多左一大堆。<br />\n各位，做文宣既要做埋這班內地生，佢地乜都唔知，叫佢地罷課無可能（佢唔x9我地已經好好），我地要做既話比佢地知發生緊乜事！我已叫自己既學生搞校內文宣，但一間學校唔夠，要靠大家！"},{"pid":"47ba8f2a01cd863791f745739f40987ffc2482f5","tid":1491877,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:22:53.000Z","msg":"阿sir你都要好好教育班學生<br />\n想當年我係我通識阿sir身上學到唔少野<br />\n你要加油呀 靠你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823約定你一齊拖手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7時集合 8時築人鏈 9時解散</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">824觀塘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">825荃葵青</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rW37Vhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrW37Vhf.jpg&h=0d9534fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzmtEJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzmtEJW.jpg&h=e1086e13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMiLGXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMiLGXg.jpg&h=6a917a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=